    "updated_at": "2024-02-21T21:34:29Z",
    "body": "Almost certainly has to do with the `terminal.integrated.minimumContrastRatio` setting, which overrides colors to ensure a minimum contrast ratio. The white text on the lighter colors (pink, yellow) fails the test so VS Code overrides the colors.",
    "author_association": "NONE",
    "pin": null,
